tiempomedio=pd.read_csv(r"C:\Users\artif\Documents\tiempopromedio.csv")
dic=pd.read_csv(r"C:\Users\artif\Documents\DiccionarioAP.csv")

if "Unnamed: 0" in MT.columns:
    MT2=MT.rename(columns={"Unnamed: 0":"mac"})
    MT.index=MT["Unnamed: 0"]
    MT=MT.drop(columns=["Unnamed: 0"])
if "mac" in tiempomedio.columns:
    tiempomedio.index=tiempomedio.mac
    tiempomedio=tiempomedio.drop(columns=["mac"])
DF1=DF[["latitude","longitude","mac"]].drop_duplicates()
if "mac" in DF1.columns:
    DF1.index=DF1.mac
    DF1=DF1.drop(columns=["mac"])
if "mac" in dic.columns:    
    dic.index=dic.mac
    dic=dic.drop(columns=["mac"])
MT1=MT.join(tiempomedio).join(DF1).join(dic.drop(columns=["latitude","longitude"])).\
rename(columns={"timean":"Tiempo promedio [min]","latitude":"Latitud","longitude":"Longitud","descripcion":"Descripción",\
                "piso":"Piso"})

import numpy as np
data=DF[["latitude","longitude","peso"]].astype(float)
DF.acctupdatetime=pd.to_datetime(DF.acctupdatetime,format="%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
data["acctupdatetime"]=DF.acctupdatetime
data1=DF[["latitude","longitude"]].drop_duplicates()
start=True

time=pd.date_range(start=DF.acctupdatetime.min().strftime("%d-%m-%Y 00:00:00"),\
                   end=DF.acctupdatetime.max().strftime("%d-%m-%Y 23:00:00"),freq="H")

for (lat,lon) in data1.values:
    data2=time.to_frame().rename(columns={0:"acctupdatetime"}).reset_index(drop=True)
    data2["latitude"]=lat
    data2["longitude"]=lon
    if start:
        data3=data2
        start=False
    else:
        data3=pd.concat([data3,data2])
        
data=data.merge(data3,on=["latitude","longitude","acctupdatetime"],how="outer").fillna(0).sort_values(["acctupdatetime"])
data["acctupdatetime"]=data.acctupdatetime.dt.strftime("%d-%m-%Y %H:%M:%S")

import folium
mapa=folium.Map(location=data1.mean(0).tolist(),control_scale=True,max_zoom=80)
sw = data1[["latitude","longitude"]].min().values.tolist()
ne = data1[["latitude","longitude"]].max().values.tolist()
mapa.fit_bounds([sw, ne]) 

for j in MT1.index:
    test = folium.Html(MT1.loc[j].drop(index=["Descripción"]).to_frame().astype(float).\
                       rename(columns={j:MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+"\n mac:"+j}).style.\
                       background_gradient(subset=pd.IndexSlice[DF.mac.unique().tolist(),MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+\
                                                                "\n mac:"+j],cmap='Blues',axis=None).\
                       format("{:.2%}",subset=pd.IndexSlice[DF.mac.unique().tolist(),MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+\
                                                                "\n mac:"+j]).render(), script=True)
    popup = folium.Popup(test, max_width=1500)
    folium.Marker(MT1.loc[j,["Latitud","Longitud"]].astype(float).tolist(), popup=popup).add_to(mapa)



import folium.plugins as plugins

df_time_list = []
dates=data.acctupdatetime.drop_duplicates().tolist()
for time in dates:
    if any(data.acctupdatetime==time):
        data1=data.loc[data.acctupdatetime==time,["latitude","longitude","peso"]]
        dat=data1[["latitude","longitude","peso"]].values.tolist()
        df_time_list.append(dat)
plugins.HeatMapWithTime(df_time_list,index=dates,auto_play=True, min_opacity=0.5, max_opacity=0.8,\
                        use_local_extrema=True,radius=30,max_speed=100,speed_step=1).add_to(mapa)

import numpy as np
data=DF[["latitude","longitude","peso"]].astype(float)
DF.acctupdatetime=pd.to_datetime(DF.acctupdatetime,format="%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
data["acctupdatetime"]=DF.acctupdatetime
data["mac"]=DF.mac
data1=DF[["latitude","longitude","mac"]].drop_duplicates()
start=True

time=pd.date_range(start=DF.acctupdatetime.min().strftime("%d-%m-%Y 00:00:00"),\
                   end=DF.acctupdatetime.max().strftime("%d-%m-%Y 23:00:00"),freq="H")

for (lat,lon,mac) in data1.values:
    data2=time.to_frame().rename(columns={0:"acctupdatetime"}).reset_index(drop=True)
    data2["latitude"]=float(lat)
    data2["longitude"]=float(lon)
    data2["mac"]=mac
    if start:
        data3=data2
        start=False
    else:
        data3=pd.concat([data3,data2])
        
data=data.merge(data3,on=["mac","latitude","longitude","acctupdatetime"],how="outer").fillna(0).\
sort_values(["acctupdatetime"])
data["acctupdatetime"]=data.acctupdatetime.dt.strftime("%d-%m-%Y %H:%M:%S")

data=data.merge(MT2,on="mac")
data[MT2.mac.tolist()]=data[MT2.mac.tolist()]*data[["peso"]*MT2.shape[0]].values
lon=data.drop(columns=MT2.mac.tolist())
lat=data.drop(columns=MT2.mac.tolist())
for m in MT2.mac:
    lon[m]=dic.loc[m,"longitude"]
    lat[m]=dic.loc[m,"latitude"]

R=np.random.ranf((lon.shape[0],MT2.shape[0]))/2
lon[MT2.mac.tolist()]=R*lon[MT2.mac.tolist()]+(1-R)*lon[["longitude"]*MT2.shape[0]].values
lat[MT2.mac.tolist()]=R*lat[MT2.mac.tolist()]+(1-R)*lat[["latitude"]*MT2.shape[0]].values

data2=data1[["latitude","longitude"]].astype(float)
import folium
mapa=folium.Map(location=data2.mean(0).tolist(),control_scale=True,max_zoom=80)
sw = data2.min(0).values.tolist()
ne = data2.max(0).values.tolist()
mapa.fit_bounds([sw, ne]) 

for j in MT1.index:
    test = folium.Html(MT1.loc[j].drop(index=["Descripción"]).to_frame().astype(float).\
                       rename(columns={j:MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+"\n mac:"+j}).style.\
                       background_gradient(subset=pd.IndexSlice[DF.mac.unique().tolist(),MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+\
                                                                "\n mac:"+j],cmap='Blues',axis=None).\
                       format("{:.2%}",subset=pd.IndexSlice[DF.mac.unique().tolist(),MT1.loc[j,"Descripción"]+\
                                                                "\n mac:"+j]).render(), script=True)
    popup = folium.Popup(test, max_width=1500)
    folium.Marker(MT1.loc[j,["Latitud","Longitud"]].astype(float).tolist(), popup=popup).add_to(mapa)

import folium.plugins as plugins
macs=MT2.mac
df_time_list = []
dates=data.acctupdatetime.drop_duplicates().tolist()
for time in dates:
    if any(data.acctupdatetime==time):
        data1=data.loc[data.acctupdatetime==time].drop(columns=["acctupdatetime"])
        lon1=lon.loc[lon.acctupdatetime==time].drop(columns=["acctupdatetime"])
        lat1=lat.loc[lon.acctupdatetime==time].drop(columns=["acctupdatetime"])
        dat=[]
        if any(data1.peso==0):
            dat+=data1.loc[data1.peso==0,["latitude","longitude","peso"]].values.tolist()
        if any(data1.peso>0):
            data3=pd.DataFrame({"peso":data1.loc[data1.peso>0,macs.tolist()].values.ravel(),
             "longitude":lon1.loc[lon1.peso>0,macs.tolist()].values.ravel(),
             "latitude":lat1.loc[lat1.peso>0,macs.tolist()].values.ravel()})
            if any(data3.peso>0):
                dat+=data3.loc[data3.peso>0,["latitude","longitude","peso"]].values.tolist()
        if dat:
            df_time_list.append(dat)
plugins.HeatMapWithTime(df_time_list,index=dates,auto_play=True, min_opacity=0.1, max_opacity=0.8,\
                        use_local_extrema=True,radius=25,max_speed=100,speed_step=1).add_to(mapa)
